title: Hypnotica - Ultimate Inner Game
description:
Ultimate Inner Game
Ultimate Inner Game

Recorded at a live "Inner Game Seminar", this 3-DVD set allows you to watch and learn directly from Hypnotica as he teaches techniques and strategies to build your Inner Game to even higher levels.

Most dating "gurus" talk about inner game, but fall far short in actually providing you with practical solutions for solving your inner game issues. With Hypnotica&#039;s "Ultimate Inner Game", you can transform your mind and emotions in just days!

For years Hypnotica has been one of the most sought-after experts due to his reputation as the "Inner Game Guru." He is known worldwide for helping men make positive and powerful changes in the way they deal with women and achieve the kind of success they&#039;ve always wanted.
